abstract: Irish Emergency Fund aids refugees and shipwreck victims in Ireland
snippet: DUBLIN, June 1 (UP)--Premier Eamon de Valera, warning tonight that Ireland is "in immediate danger," said that the nation had only "days, not weeks or months" in which to prepare against the threat of embroilment in the European war....

headline.main: DE VALERA WARNS OF PERIL TO IRELAND; Calls on Nation to Prepare to Repel Invasion

lead_paragraph: DUBLIN, June 1 (UP)--Premier Eamon de Valera, warning tonight that Ireland is "in immediate danger," said that the nation had only "days, not weeks or months" in which to prepare against the threat of embroilment in the European war.
